Copenhagen in 1912.

00:11:49.900 --> 00:11:52.130
Movies are now big business.

00:11:52.130 --> 00:11:56.990
Thousands and thousands of people
want to see them around the world.

00:11:56.990 --> 00:11:58.840
Reflecting the same
thing is the emergence

00:11:58.840 --> 00:12:00.540
