00:12:00.540 --> 00:12:04.510
In fact, all the things now, we
think of as part of, you know,

00:12:04.510 --> 00:12:09.400
movie buzz, the movie world being
a standard file, start that.

00:12:09.400 --> 00:12:12.230
You have the rise of film
culture as the film press.

