00:12:20.220 --> 00:12:21.670
Same as through in other countries.

00:12:21.670 --> 00:12:26.100
In the USA, you'd start
to have trade papers,

00:12:26.100 --> 00:12:29.910
newspapers devoted just to the film
business, Moving Picture World,

