00:56:50.690 --> 00:56:54.200
on the street, all these
people I owe a lot.

00:56:54.200 --> 00:56:57.980
I really have benefited
enormously from my stay here.

00:56:57.980 --> 00:57:00.680
I'm grateful for-- to the
Kluge center for inviting me

00:57:00.680 --> 00:57:03.090
to participate in their
