00:57:11.710 --> 00:57:13.060
I really have enjoyed my stay here.

00:57:13.060 --> 00:57:14.540
I wish it could go on forever.

00:57:14.540 --> 00:57:16.070
But thank you for your attention.

00:57:16.070 --> 00:57:18.960
And of course, I'm happy
